dimension when a young woman discovers the remnants of an ancient cult beneath

in the Ray Harryhausen tradition and writer/director Brett Piper's visual flair 
brings this adaptation of H.P. Lovecraft's DREAMS IN THE WITCH HOUSE to vibrant
